ul>\n<li>hunspell</li>\n<li>aspell</li>\n<li>myspell</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Here’s how to install Canadian English in *Ubuntu.</p>\n<pre><code>sudo apt-get install hunspell-en-ca\n</code></pre>\n<p>Close/reopen LibreOffice and that’s it! :D</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"LibreOffice Spell Check Not Working","date":"January 09, 2014","description":"I'm a computer tech, originally from Toronto, hold a recent degree and offer lots of experience. It'd be great to try something new, like analytics, but my current lot is still a good one and puts food on the table. If you're interested, please take a look at the links below!"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/spell-check/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/senor-woof/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Senor Woof"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/ghost-openshift2-mac/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Setting Up Ghost on OpenShift using Mac OS X"}}}}}